{'type': 'chat_message', 'role': {'type': 'role', 'value': 'user'}, 'contents': [{'type': 'text', 'text': '**Business Proposal: AI-Powered Customer Service for Banks**  \n**Prepared: 18 June 2026**\n\n**Executive Summary**  \nDeploy a multi-agent AI system to handle 70-80% of routine customer queries 24/7, reduce average handling time by 45%, and improve CSAT scores by 20-30 points while staying fully compliant.\n\n**Current Pain Points**  \n- Long wait times and repetitive queries (balance, transfers, card blocks)  \n- High agent turnover and training costs  \n- Inconsistent advice and compliance risk\n\n**Proposed Solution**  \nA modular ReAct + multi-agent platform with three specialized agents:  \n- Intent & Routing Agent (classifies query)  \n- Knowledge & Tool Agent (retrieves policies, executes actions via bank APIs)  \n- Compliance & Escalation Agent (enforces rules, detects anomalies, hands off to human)  \n\n**High-Level Architecture**  \n```\nCustomer (chat/app) \n    \u2193\n[Router Agent] \u2192 [Knowledge Agent] \u2192 Bank Core APIs (KYC, ledger)\n    \u2193                                    \u2193\n[Compliance Agent] \u2190 Logging & Audit DB\n    \u2193\nHuman Agent (escalation) + Feedback Loop\n```\n\n**Key Technical Components**  \n- LLM backbone with tool-calling (ReAct loop + parallel tool execution)  \n- Short-term memory (Redis) + long-term policy vector store  \n- Guardrails: PII redaction, hallucination checks, hard caps (max 8 turns)  \n- Integration via secure APIs + SOC 2 / GDPR-ready logging\n\n**Expected ROI (per 1M customers/year)**  \n- Cost savings: $2.8–4.2 M (agent FTE reduction)  \n- Revenue uplift: $1.1 M (faster resolution \u2192 higher product uptake)  \n- Payback: 7–9 months  \n- CSAT: +25 points, NPS +18\n\n**Implementation Roadmap**  \n- Month 1-2: Pilot on 3 query types (balance, card block, transfers)  \n- Month 3-4: Full ReAct deployment + parallel tools + human handoff  \n- Month 5-6: Monitoring, A/B testing, model fine-tuning  \n- Ongoing: Quarterly compliance audits\n\n**Risks & Mitigations**  \n- Hallucination \u2192 mandatory retrieval + human override threshold  \n- Data leakage \u2192 on-prem or private-cloud deployment + redaction layer  \n- Compliance \u2192 built-in'}], 'additional_properties': {}}
